snippet.title: Amiga Longplay Unreal
snippet.description:
http://www.recordedamigagames.org

Played By: Lemm

This game is such a nice one. Very nice music, sound FX and grafix you are enyoing in the present, too. Maybe the sword fighting looks a little bit like freshman.

The intro duration takes 6 minutes of movie lenght. -
